<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Manuales y Documentación — Appogio</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Documentación completa de todas las aplicaciones Appogio: guías de inicio, manuales de usuario y tutoriales paso a paso.">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 32 32'><rect width='32' height='32' rx='8' fill='%230EA5E9'/><text x='16' y='22' text-anchor='middle' font-family='system-ui' font-weight='900' font-size='18' fill='white'>A</text></svg>">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/css/main.css">
  <style>
    .search-highlight { background: rgba(14,165,233,.2); border-radius: 3px; padding: 0 2px; }
    .manual-card { display: block; text-decoration: none; }
    .manual-card:hover .manual-card-title { color: var(--c-text); }
    .manual-card-title { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 800; font-family: var(--font-head); margin-bottom: .375rem; color: var(--c-text); transition: var(--t-fast); }
    .tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      padding: .2rem .6rem;
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-size: .7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.06);
      color: var(--c-text-3);
      margin-bottom: .875rem;
    }
    .section-tabs {
      display: flex;
      gap: .75rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .section-tab {
      padding: .5rem 1.25rem;
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-size: .825rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--c-border-2);
      color: var(--c-text-2);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: var(--t-fast);
    }
    .section-tab.active, .section-tab:hover {
      border-color: var(--c-accent);
      color: var(--c-accent);
      background: var(--c-accent-glow);
    }

    /* ── Manual Drawer ── */
    .manual-overlay {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,.55);
      z-index: 9000;
      opacity: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      transition: opacity .25s ease;
    }
    .manual-overlay.open {
      opacity: 1;
      pointer-events: all;
    }
    .manual-drawer {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 480px;
      max-width: 100vw;
      background: #0F172A;
      border-left: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      z-index: 9001;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      transform: translateX(100%);
      transition: transform .3s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .manual-drawer.open {
      transform: translateX(0);
    }
    .drawer-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1.75rem 1.75rem 1.25rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .drawer-app-icon {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .drawer-header-text { flex: 1; }
    .drawer-app-name {
      font-size: .75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .06em;
      color: var(--c-text-3);
      margin-bottom: .25rem;
    }
    .drawer-topic-title {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-family: var(--font-head, system-ui);
      color: #F1F5F9;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }
    .drawer-close {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);
      background: none;
      color: #94A3B8;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      transition: background .15s, color .15s;
    }
    .drawer-close:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,.06); color: #F1F5F9; }
    .drawer-body {
      flex: 1;
      overflow-y: auto;
      padding: 1.75rem;
    }
    .drawer-steps { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem; }
    .drawer-step {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .step-num {
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      font-size: .8rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: .05rem;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .step-text {
      font-size: .925rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
      color: #CBD5E1;
      padding-top: .2rem;
    }
    .drawer-footer {
      padding: 1.25rem 1.75rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .drawer-footer p {
      font-size: .8rem;
      color: var(--c-text-3);
      margin: 0 0 .75rem;
    }
    .drawer-footer a {
      font-size: .825rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--c-accent, #0EA5E9);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .drawer-footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    @media (max-width: 520px) {
      .manual-drawer { width: 100vw; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="navbar scrolled">
  <div class="container">
    <a href="../index.html" class="nav-logo"><img src="../assets/images/logo-appogio.png?v=2" height="38" alt="Appogio" style="display:block;"></a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="../index.html#features" class="nav-link">Plataforma</a>
      <a href="../index.html#apps" class="nav-link">Aplicaciones</a>
      <a href="index.html" class="nav-link" style="color:var(--c-text)">Manuales</a>
      <a href="../contacto.html" class="nav-link">Contacto</a>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-cta"><a href="../contacto.html" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm">Solicitar Demo</a></div>
    <button class="nav-mobile-toggle" aria-label="Menú"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16"/></svg></button>
  </div>
</nav>
<div class="mobile-menu">
  <a href="../index.html">Inicio</a><a href="../index.html#apps">Aplicaciones</a>
  <a href="index.html">Manuales</a><a href="../contacto.html">Contacto</a>
</div>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="manuals-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div data-reveal>
      <span class="section-label" style="display:inline-flex">Documentación</span>
      <h1>Manuales y <span class="gradient-text">Guías</span></h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.125rem;color:var(--c-text-2);max-width:500px;margin:.75rem auto 0">Todo lo que necesitas para configurar, operar y sacar el máximo provecho de cada aplicación Appogio.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="manuals-search" data-reveal>
      <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" style="color:var(--c-text-3);flex-shrink:0"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/></svg>
      <input type="text" placeholder="Buscar en los manuales… (ej: &quot;firma digital&quot;, &quot;geocerca&quot;)" id="search-input" oninput="filterManuals(this.value)">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Tabs de categoría -->
<section class="section" style="padding-top:3rem">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-tabs">
      <button class="section-tab active" onclick="filterCategory('all', this)">Todos</button>
      <button class="section-tab" onclick="filterCategory('plataforma', this)">Plataforma GPS</button>
      <button class="section-tab" onclick="filterCategory('inspectpro', this)">InspectPro</button>
      <button class="section-tab" onclick="filterCategory('driveiq', this)">DriveIQ</button>
      <button class="section-tab" onclick="filterCategory('pilotos', this)">PilotOS</button>
      <button class="section-tab" onclick="filterCategory('camfleet', this)">CamFleet</button>
      <button class="section-tab" onclick="filterCategory('tagradar', this)">TagRadar</button>
      <button class="section-tab" onclick="filterCategory('notice', this)">Notice</button>
    </div>

    <!-- Cards de manuales -->
    <div class="manuals-grid" id="manuals-grid">

      <!-- Plataforma GPS -->
      <div class="manual-card" data-category="plataforma" id="plataforma">
        <div style="background:var(--c-bg-card);border:1px solid var(--c-border);border-radius:var(--radius-xl);padding:2rem;transition:var(--t-base)">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.875rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem">
            <div style="width:48px;height:48px;background:rgba(14,165,233,.1);border:1px solid rgba(14,165,233,.2);border-radius:var(--radius);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0EA5E9" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M12 2v3M12 19v3M2 12h3M19 12h3"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="tag" style="color:#0EA5E9">Plataforma</div>
              <div class="manual-card-title">Monitoreo GPS</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="manual-sections">
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#0EA5E9" onclick="openManual('plataforma',0)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Primeros pasos y configuración</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#0EA5E9" onclick="openManual('plataforma',1)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Agregar vehículos y dispositivos</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#0EA5E9" onclick="openManual('plataforma',2)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Configurar geocercas y alertas</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#0EA5E9" onclick="openManual('plataforma',3)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Generar reportes de recorridos</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#0EA5E9" onclick="openManual('plataforma',4)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Gestión de usuarios y permisos</a>
          </div>
          <a href="../contacto.html" class="app-card-link" style="--app-color:#0EA5E9">Ver manual completo <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- InspectPro -->
      <div class="manual-card" data-category="inspectpro" id="inspectpro">
        <div style="background:var(--c-bg-card);border:1px solid var(--c-border);border-radius:var(--radius-xl);padding:2rem;transition:var(--t-base)">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.875rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem">
            <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:var(--radius);overflow:hidden;flex-shrink:0">
              <img src="../assets/images/icons/inspectpro.png" width="48" height="48" alt="InspectPro" style="display:block;object-fit:cover;width:100%;height:100%">
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="tag" style="color:#3B82F6">Aplicación</div>
              <div class="manual-card-title">InspectPro</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="manual-sections">
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#3B82F6" onclick="openManual('inspectpro',0)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Crear tu primera plantilla</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#3B82F6" onclick="openManual('inspectpro',1)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Completar inspecciones (conductor)</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#3B82F6" onclick="openManual('inspectpro',2)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Flujo de aprobación (supervisor)</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#3B82F6" onclick="openManual('inspectpro',3)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Firma digital y reporte PDF</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#3B82F6" onclick="openManual('inspectpro',4)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Dashboard de cumplimiento</a>
          </div>
          <a href="../apps/inspectpro.html" class="app-card-link" style="--app-color:#3B82F6">Ver página de InspectPro <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- DriveIQ -->
      <div class="manual-card" data-category="driveiq" id="driveiq">
        <div style="background:var(--c-bg-card);border:1px solid var(--c-border);border-radius:var(--radius-xl);padding:2rem;transition:var(--t-base)">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.875rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem">
            <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:var(--radius);overflow:hidden;flex-shrink:0">
              <img src="../assets/images/icons/driveiq.svg" width="48" height="48" alt="DriveIQ" style="display:block;object-fit:cover;width:100%;height:100%">
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="tag" style="color:#F59E0B">Aplicación</div>
              <div class="manual-card-title">DriveIQ</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="manual-sections">
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#F59E0B" onclick="openManual('driveiq',0)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Configurar análisis de conducción</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#F59E0B" onclick="openManual('driveiq',1)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Entender el score de conductor</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#F59E0B" onclick="openManual('driveiq',2)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Tipos de eventos registrados</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#F59E0B" onclick="openManual('driveiq',3)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Ranking y comparativas</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#F59E0B" onclick="openManual('driveiq',4)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Exportar reportes de comportamiento</a>
          </div>
          <a href="../apps/driveiq.html" class="app-card-link" style="--app-color:#F59E0B">Ver página de DriveIQ <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- PilotOS -->
      <div class="manual-card" data-category="pilotos" id="pilotos">
        <div style="background:var(--c-bg-card);border:1px solid var(--c-border);border-radius:var(--radius-xl);padding:2rem;transition:var(--t-base)">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.875rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem">
            <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:var(--radius);overflow:hidden;flex-shrink:0">
              <img src="../assets/images/icons/pilotos.png" width="48" height="48" alt="PilotOS" style="display:block;object-fit:cover;width:100%;height:100%">
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="tag" style="color:#8B5CF6">Aplicación</div>
              <div class="manual-card-title">PilotOS</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="manual-sections">
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#8B5CF6" onclick="openManual('pilotos',0)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Registrar un conductor</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#8B5CF6" onclick="openManual('pilotos',1)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Check-in y check-out por QR</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#8B5CF6" onclick="openManual('pilotos',2)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Gestionar documentos y vencimientos</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#8B5CF6" onclick="openManual('pilotos',3)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Enviar mensajes a conductores</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#8B5CF6" onclick="openManual('pilotos',4)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Reportes de asistencia y turnos</a>
          </div>
          <a href="../apps/pilotos.html" class="app-card-link" style="--app-color:#8B5CF6">Ver página de PilotOS <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CamFleet -->
      <div class="manual-card" data-category="camfleet" id="camfleet">
        <div style="background:var(--c-bg-card);border:1px solid var(--c-border);border-radius:var(--radius-xl);padding:2rem;transition:var(--t-base)">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.875rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem">
            <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:var(--radius);overflow:hidden;flex-shrink:0">
              <img src="../assets/images/icons/camfleet.svg" width="48" height="48" alt="CamFleet" style="display:block;object-fit:cover;width:100%;height:100%">
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="tag" style="color:#EF4444">Aplicación</div>
              <div class="manual-card-title">CamFleet</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="manual-sections">
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#EF4444" onclick="openManual('camfleet',0)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Instalar y configurar cámaras</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#EF4444" onclick="openManual('camfleet',1)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Ver streaming en vivo</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#EF4444" onclick="openManual('camfleet',2)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Reproducir y descargar grabaciones</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#EF4444" onclick="openManual('camfleet',3)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Configurar alertas de eventos</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#EF4444" onclick="openManual('camfleet',4)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Exportar evidencia con metadatos</a>
          </div>
          <a href="../apps/camfleet.html" class="app-card-link" style="--app-color:#EF4444">Ver página de CamFleet <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- TagRadar -->
      <div class="manual-card" data-category="tagradar" id="tagradar">
        <div style="background:var(--c-bg-card);border:1px solid var(--c-border);border-radius:var(--radius-xl);padding:2rem;transition:var(--t-base)">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.875rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem">
            <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:var(--radius);overflow:hidden;flex-shrink:0">
              <img src="../assets/images/icons/tagradar.svg" width="48" height="48" alt="TagRadar" style="display:block;object-fit:cover;width:100%;height:100%">
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="tag" style="color:#10B981">Aplicación</div>
              <div class="manual-card-title">TagRadar</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="manual-sections">
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#10B981" onclick="openManual('tagradar',0)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Registrar activos y asignar tags</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#10B981" onclick="openManual('tagradar',1)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Configurar lectores BLE</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#10B981" onclick="openManual('tagradar',2)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Crear zonas y geocercas de activos</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#10B981" onclick="openManual('tagradar',3)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Alertas de salida y batería baja</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#10B981" onclick="openManual('tagradar',4)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Reportes de utilización</a>
          </div>
          <a href="../apps/tagradar.html" class="app-card-link" style="--app-color:#10B981">Ver página de TagRadar <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Notice -->
      <div class="manual-card" data-category="notice" id="notice">
        <div style="background:var(--c-bg-card);border:1px solid var(--c-border);border-radius:var(--radius-xl);padding:2rem;transition:var(--t-base)">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.875rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem">
            <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:var(--radius);overflow:hidden;flex-shrink:0">
              <img src="../assets/images/icons/notice.png" width="48" height="48" alt="Notice" style="display:block;object-fit:cover;width:100%;height:100%">
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="tag" style="color:#06B6D4">Aplicación</div>
              <div class="manual-card-title">Notice</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="manual-sections">
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#06B6D4" onclick="openManual('notice',0)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Conectar WhatsApp Business</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#06B6D4" onclick="openManual('notice',1)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Crear reglas de alerta GPS</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#06B6D4" onclick="openManual('notice',2)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Enviar mensajes masivos</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#06B6D4" onclick="openManual('notice',3)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Crear plantillas de mensajes</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="manual-section-link" style="--app-color:#06B6D4" onclick="openManual('notice',4)"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>Revisar historial de envíos</a>
          </div>
          <a href="../apps/notice.html" class="app-card-link" style="--app-color:#06B6D4">Ver página de Notice <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div><!-- /manuals-grid -->

    <!-- No encuentras lo que buscas -->
    <div style="background:var(--c-bg-card);border:1px solid var(--c-border);border-radius:var(--radius-xl);padding:3rem;text-align:center;margin-top:3rem" data-reveal>
      <div style="width:48px;height:48px;background:rgba(14,165,233,.1);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 1rem">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0EA5E9" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 01-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 style="margin-bottom:.625rem">¿No encuentras lo que buscas?</h3>
      <p style="max-width:440px;margin:0 auto 1.75rem">Nuestro equipo de soporte responde en menos de 4 horas hábiles. También puedes contactarnos directamente.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap">
        <a href="../contacto.html" class="btn btn-primary">Contactar soporte</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

